quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,15,"Waalqa fee al-ardi rawasiyaan tameeda bikum waanharan wasubulan laAAallakum tahtadoon"
  16,16,"WaAAalamatin wabinnajmihum yahtadoon"
  16,17,"Afaman yakhluqu kaman la yakhluquafala tathakkaroon"
  16,18,"Wa-in taAAuddoo niAAmata Allahi latuhsooha inna Allaha laghafoorun raheem"
  16,19,"Wallahu yaAAlamu matusirroona wama tuAAlinoon"
  16,20,"Wallatheena yadAAoona mindooni Allahi la yakhluqoona shay-an wahumyukhlaqoon"
  16,21,"Amwatun ghayru ahya-inwama yashAAuroona ayyana yubAAathoon"
  16,22,"Ilahukum ilahun wahidunfallatheena la yu/minoona bil-akhiratiquloobuhum munkiratun wahum mustakbiroon"
  16,23,"La jarama anna Allaha yaAAlamuma yusirroona wama yuAAlinoona innahu la yuhibbualmustakbireen"
  16,24,"Wa-itha qeela lahum mathaanzala rabbukum qaloo asateeru al-awwaleen"
  16,25,"Liyahmiloo awzarahum kamilatanyawma alqiyamati wamin awzari allatheena yudilloonahumbighayri AAilmin ala saa ma yaziroon"
  16,26,"Qad makara allatheena min qablihimfaata Allahu bunyanahum mina alqawaAAidifakharra AAalayhimu assaqfu min fawqihim waatahumualAAathabu min haythu la yashAAuroon"
